 under the rule.\\\"}\n\nThus we need to write:\n\n<parameter=args>\n{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted evidence shows Iran issued NOTAM A1010/26 suspending all civil flight permits and closing airports in western Tehran FIR, with flight-tracking data indicating commercial aircraft rerouted away. This constitutes a broad suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region, satisfying the rule's major-closure prong. Limited exceptions (daylight, per-flight approval) do not disqualify the closure under the rule.\\\"}\n</parameter>\n\nNow let's try that.\n\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_085cda1331dee2ea","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted evidence shows Iran issued NOTAM A1010/26 suspending all civil flight permits and closing airports in western Tehran FIR, with flight-tracking data indicating commercial aircraft rerouted away. This constitutes a broad suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region, satisfying the rule's major-closure prong. Limited exceptions (daylight, per-flight approval) do not disqualify the closure under the rule.\\\"}"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\\\\\"vote\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"demonstrated\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"rationale\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"The admitted evidence shows Iran issued NOTAM A1010/26 suspending all civil flight permits and closing airports in western Tehran FIR, with flight-tracking data indicating commercial aircraft rerouted away. This constitutes a broad suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region, satisfying the rule's major-closure prong. Limited exceptions (daylight, per-flight approval) do not disqualify the closure under the rule.\\\\\\\"}\"}","streamIn