10/26 suspending all civil flight permits and closing airports in western Tehran FIR, with flight-tracking data indicating commercial aircraft rerouted away. This constitutes a broad suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region, satisfying the rule's major-closure prong. Limited exceptions (daylight, per-flight approval) do not disqualify the closure under the rule.\\\"}\n\u003c/parameter\u003e\n\nNow we need to ensure that the content between the tags is exactly that string, including the backslashes before the double quotes.\n\nLet's write that.\n\nI'll now write the args content as:\n\n{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted evidence shows Iran issued NOTAM A1010/26 suspending all civil flight permits and closing airports in western Tehran FIR, with flight-tracking data indicating commercial aircraft rerouted away. This constitutes a broad suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region, satisfying the rule's major-closure prong. Limited exceptions (daylight, per-flight approval) do not disqualify the closure under the rule.\\\"}\n\nNow put that inside \u003cparameter=args\u003e and \u003c/parameter\u003e.\n\nLet's do it.\n\n\n","contentIndex":0,"partial":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"reasoning","type":"thinking"},{"arguments":{"args":"{'vote': 'demonstrated', 'rationale': \"The admitted evidence shows Iran issued NOTAM A1010/26 suspending all civil flight permits and closing airports in western Tehran FIR, with flight-tracking data indicating commercial aircraft rerouted away. This constitutes a broad suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region, satisfying the rule's major-closure prong. Limited exceptions (daylight, per-flight approval) do not disqualify the closure under the rule.\"}","tool":"aar_submit_counc