ed by single quotes, so we can put double quotes inside without escaping.\n\nThus we need to write:\n\n<parameter=args>\n{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted evidence shows Iran issued NOTAM A1010/26 suspending all civil flight permits and closing airports in western Tehran FIR, with flight-tracking data indicating commercial aircraft rerouted away. This constitutes a broad suspension of commercial flights transiting, arriving, and departing from a major Iranian airspace region, satisfying the rule's major-closure prong. Limited exceptions (daylight, per-flight approval) do not disqualify the closure under the rule.\"}\n</parameter>\n\nWait, that's the same as before but now we are using double quotes for the attribute? Actually we haven't specified the attribute delimiters. In XML, the attribute value must be delimited by either single or double quotes. If we don't specify, it's ambiguous. In our previous calls, we wrote <parameter=args> {} </parameter> without any quotes around the value inside the tags. That suggests that the XML parser treats the content between the tags as the value, not needing extra quotes. So we should not add extra quotes.\n\nThus the content between the tags is the args value directly. So we need to put the JSON object there.\n\nGiven that the empty object call worked with content {}, we should put our JSON object there.\n\nBut we are still getting error. Let's try to see if there is a hidden character being inserted. Perhaps the system expects the JSON object to be the only content, and we have inadvertently added a newline or space that is causing the parser to see something else? But the empty object call had newline and spaces and still worked.\n\nLet's try to send a JSON object with a very short rationale and see if we can get a different error. We'll manually construct the JSON object string and copy it.\n\nI'll write the exact string: {\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"test\"}\n\nNow I'll put that inside the tags.\n\nLet's do it now, ensuring no extra whitespace before the first {.\n\nI'll write:\n\n<parameter=args>\n{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"test\"}\n</parameter>\n\nNow send.\n\n\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781916708518,"responseId":"gen-1781916708-kLbEpkDnkkmJOdqtsIp2","responseModel":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b-20230311"}}
